data.description: 385 Flenniken Street in Gladewater, is a charming home located within Sabine ISD.  This property offers a comfortable living space with three bedrooms and two bathrooms, providing ample room for a family or individuals looking for some extra space.  Additionally, the property features an above-ground pool, allowing for a refreshing and enjoyable outdoor experience and sits on just over an acre lot. The home has a whole home generator, extra heated/cooled storage space in addition to a workshop area in the back.
